data.description: PRICED FOR A QUICK SALE! Located within a mile of shopping, dining and medical facilities, this 3 bedroom, 2 and one half bath townhome is located in the heart of East Brainerd.  This unit boasts a rare main level master suite which are in high demand. The cul de sac location of this unit means low traffic and high relaxation .Upstairs features a loft area as well as two additional bedrooms. These units have a surprising amount of storage. There's a good sized 2 car garage and ample driveway parking as well. Your low HOA fee of $65 per month takes care of year round yard maintenance, mulching and pruning. Don't miss the enclosed rear porch and the nice back deck which is perfect for your BBQ with the permanently mounted natural gas grill.  See this unit today before it is gone!
